29
00:01:32,001 --> 00:01:40,905
About three years ago, Chad left to me and asked me about starting a program helping the veterans that needed repairs.

30
00:01:41,245 --> 00:01:45,066
And since then, it's grown into something that's been pretty good.

31
00:01:45,987 --> 00:01:51,409
Anytime I've called Chad and his friends, they've been there to help out a veteran or a veteran's family in need.

32
00:01:52,350 --> 00:01:53,210
On this particular one,

33
00:01:54,548 --> 00:02:01,894
