38
00:02:24,562 --> 00:02:29,264
His house is a raised ranch, and he's probably about 10 or 15 feet off the ground.

39
00:02:29,964 --> 00:02:36,065
And guy hadn't been out of the house in a couple of years, and every time he goes out, it costs about $385 to go out by ambulance.

40
00:02:37,045 --> 00:02:49,548
So we go in there, we explain to the guy that, you know, this is really not what we do, you know, it's kind of a little bit over our head, you know, funds and everything, but we'd look into it and maybe see if we can find him, you know, something or another agency to go to.

41
00:02:50,108 --> 00:02:51,609
So we left, and Chad,

42
00:02:53,002 --> 00:02:54,823
