44
00:03:07,010 --> 00:03:10,251
He says, I found you a lift on the House on Gordy Road.

45
00:03:11,372 --> 00:03:15,094
He said a friend of his they knew was over there had passed away and the house had been sold.

46
00:03:15,594 --> 00:03:20,237
I went over there and I met the people, nice people, the Morris's.

47
00:03:21,195 --> 00:03:25,018
And I asked them if they would be kind enough to donate the lift to them.

48
00:03:25,678 --> 00:03:26,679
