50
00:03:28,280 --> 00:03:28,780
He came down.

51
00:03:28,820 --> 00:03:29,280
We looked at it.

52
00:03:29,300 --> 00:03:30,001
We thought we could do it.

53
00:03:31,061 --> 00:03:34,043
